thread.title: Natalie Oties
thread.title_full: Choice Home Warranty reviewed by Natalie Oties

author: Natalie Oties
title: Natalie Oties
text: The Repair company came to access the problem with my garbage disposal in a timely manner. The repairman determined that I needed a new one and promised to bring it and install it the next day. As promised, my new unit was installed. I am very pleased with the attention, given to me, by CHW and would recommend them to a friend.
